# TDD 提交訊息模板
# 請依照 Red-Green-Refactor 循環選擇適當的前綴
#
# 🔴 RED 階段 - 撰寫失敗測試
# red: add failing test for [功能描述]
#
# 🟢 GREEN 階段 - 實現最少程式碼讓測試通過
# green: implement [功能] to pass tests
#
# 🔵 REFACTOR 階段 - 改善程式碼結構
# refactor: extract [邏輯] to [目標位置]
# refactor: rename [舊名稱] to [新名稱] for clarity
# refactor: optimize [功能] performance
#
# 📝 其他類型
# test: add unit tests for [功能]
# feat: implement [新功能] (僅用於非 TDD 流程)
# fix: resolve [問題描述]
# docs: update documentation for [內容]
#
# TDD 最佳實踐提醒：
# - 每次提交應該很小且專注
# - Red 提交只包含失敗的測試
# - Green 提交只實現讓測試通過的最少程式碼
# - Refactor 提交不改變功能行為
# - 提交前確保所有測試都通過
#
# 範例：
# red: add failing test for user login validation
# green: implement login validation to pass tests
# refactor: extract validation logic to UserValidator service
